<title>CHINA: COMPANION BUILD YEAR NET DOWN 20.56 PCT.</title>
<headline>COMPANION BUILD YEAR NET DOWN 20.56 PCT.</headline>
<dateline>HONG KONG 1997-08-12</dateline>
<text>
<p>Year ended March 31</p>
<p>(in million HK$ unless stated)</p>
<p>    Shr (H.K. cents)	   5.00	 vs 7.64 (adjusted)</p>
<p>    Dividend (H.K. cents)    0.5	  vs 2.5</p>
<p>    Exceptional items	  29.53 gain vs 14.40 gain</p>
<p>    Net			    72.31	vs 91.03</p>
<p>    Turnover		     1,000.44   vs 939.92</p>
<p>    Company name		 Companion Building Material</p>
<p>				     (Holdings) Ltd</p>
<p>    Books close		  September 10-16</p>
<p>    Dividend payable	   December 10</p>
<p>NOTE - Companion Building Materials makes and distributes ceramic tiles, marble and granite products.</p>
<p>Net is after an exceptional gain on deemed disposal of interest in Companion Marble (Holdings) Ltd.</p>
<p>Comparative share earnings have been adjusted for bonus issues of one-for-five shares and one-for-one share in 1996.</p>
<p>Total dividend for year is two H.K. cents (including interim dividend of 1.5 cents) vs 4.5 cents.</p>
<p>-- Hong Kong News Room (852) 2843 6368</p>
